<h2>How It Works</h2>
<p>The system reads data from an Excel spreadsheet, calculates portfolio returns, and presents them in an interactive table and chart format.</p>

<h2>Key Features</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Compare portfolio returns over different time periods.</li>
    <li>Graphical analysis of portfolio performance.</li>
    <li>Track return history over time.</li>
</ul>

